{"tid":2026532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：如果你曾經患過普通感冒，你對於新冠狀病毒covid-19，已經有了抵抗力。","createTime":"2020-05-21T04:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T11:41:32.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d7147b47d9cd9bb424d8f5c274a892f444ae5d84","tid":2026532,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"陳雲：各國解封之前，外國醫學界證明，新冠狀病毒也是冠狀病毒的一種，即是那些引起普通感冒的冠狀病毒。故此，如果你曾經患過普通感冒，你對於新冠狀病毒covid-19，已經有了抵抗力。<br />\n你一世人之中，有無患感冒過呢？不要告訴我，你沒有啊。<br />\n從去年十二月開始，這是陳雲一直在轉告香港人的國際醫學常識。現在，要勞《細胞》雜誌告訴各位。<br />\n香港人，鳩戴口罩吧，經濟衰退啊。香港政府有無能力量化寬鬆和壓低利息呢？<br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情：科學家稱患過普通感冒或為你提供一些保護<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-52725910?fbclid=IwAR172B1fc8C5BvVvZcnanKi4qJUKSPJBQTsicLGk5d3ZFiarAiKX_tEcV00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-52725910%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR172B1fc8C5BvVvZcnanKi4qJUKSPJBQTsicLGk5d3ZFiarAiKX_tEcV00&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsdg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=5c3bc6c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-52725910%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR172B1fc8C5BvVvZcnanKi4qJUKSPJBQTsicLGk5d3ZFiarAiKX_tEcV00&h=f078537b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-52725910?fbclid=IwAR172B1fc8C5BvVvZcnanKi4qJUKSPJBQTsicLGk5d3ZFiarAiKX_tEcV00</a>"},{"pid":"793984aa416bfcccfc6d6e24a605489c26756664","tid":2026532,"uid":357636,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:23:03.000Z","msg":"銀離子繼續滯銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d865e517aeae133043008a11165a8dca3f815353","tid":2026532,"uid":113547,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"全世界有500萬人無患過感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ecaf5d7c7232a590bed92bf